# Trivy suppressions for the image scans in .github/workflows/ci.yml.
#
# The gate already passes `--ignore-unfixed`, so anything that lands here is a
# CVE that HAS an upstream fix but that we are consciously accepting for now.
# Every entry must have an owner and an expiry - an empty file is a good sign.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-2026-12345 exp:2026-12-31   # why, who owns it
#
# (no active suppressions)
